    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels at MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at Gradation 1 for MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied across all five evaluated operating points.",
